item.title: What would you change about pytest?
item.description: Anthony Sottile and Brian discuss changes that would be cool for pytest, even unrealistic changes. These are changes we'd make to pytest if we didn't ahve to care about backwards compatibilty. Feed: https://testandcode.com/rss
